static get observedAttributes() {
    return [
        'title', 'size', 'variant', 'animation', 'direction', 
        'duration', 'bg-color', 'color', 'open', 'backdrop-close', 
        'keyboard-close', 'auto-focus', 'modal-class', 'z-index', 'offset'
    ];
}
```

#### 5. **Failed Container Detection**
